<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>BRUTAG | Ropa usada hombre</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #0b0b0b;
      color: white;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200, 169, 107, 0.25);
      padding: 22px 26px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
      color: #f5f1eb;
      font-size: 42px;
      letter-spacing: 10px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .logo span {
      color: #c8a96b;
    }

    .header-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .header-actions a {
      color: #c8a96b;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 90px 28px 70px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(200, 169, 107, 0.12), transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #050505, #121212 55%, #080808);
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      color: #c8a96b;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .badge::before {
      content: "";
      width: 70px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #c8a96b;
      display: block;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 96px;
      line-height: 0.92;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 span {
      color: #c8a96b;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #9f9f9f;
      max-width: 620px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 46px;
    }

    .product-section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .product-images {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .product-images img {
      width: 100%;
      background: white;
      padding: 10px;
      display: block;
    }

    .product-card {
      border: 1px solid rgba(200, 169, 107, 0.3);
      padding: 28px;
      background: #111;
    }

    .product-card h2 {
      font-size: 34px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #c8a96b;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .product-card p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #d0d0d0;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 42px !important;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #c8a96b !important;
      margin: 18px 0 24px !important;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #c8a96b;
      color: black;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 18px 32px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: white;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 34px;
        letter-spacing: 7px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 64px;
      }

      .intro {
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .product-section {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .product-images {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">BRUT<span>AG</span></div>
    <div class="header-actions">
      <a href="https://instagram.com/brutag__" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="badge">Ropa usada para hombre</div>
      <h1>Viste <span>con</span><br>fuerza</h1>
      <p class="intro">Solo ropa usada para hombre. Prendas seleccionadas, urbanas y con estilo.</p>

      <section class="product-section">
        <div class="product-images">
          <img src="DF714C16-A2E6-441B-95F2-5F4ECA819392.jpeg" alt="Polerón Grizzly frente">
          <img src="5664C4BE-44AF-4AD2-9D0F-12CC1354FB4E.jpeg" alt="Polerón Grizzly espalda">
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
          <h2>Polerón Grizzly</h2>
          <p>Talla XL · Ropa usada de hombre seleccionada.</p>
          <p>Prenda urbana, simple y fuerte para vestir con presencia.</p>
          <p class="price">$20.000</p>
          <a class="btn" href="https://instagram.com/brutag__" target="_blank">Comprar por Instagram</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
